  "text": "The rest of the paper is organized as follows. Section 2 reviews the relevant literature. We introduce datasets and evaluation protocol in Sec. 3. We benchmark our baseline in Sec. 4. We test the generalization capabilities of the baseline in Sec. [CITATION_1] . We discuss about current state-of-the-art along Section 6 and finally, conclude the paper in Section 7.",
  "correct_citation": {
